title: West Ham defeat heaps more misery on Jose Mourinho's Chelsea (PFA - Professional Footballers' Association) ...
text: ( Source : PFA - Professional Footballers' Association ) Jose Mourinho was sent to the stands as Chelsea's dreadful season hit a new low in a 2-1 defeat at West Ham . Andy Carroll 's second-half header condemned the Blues to a fifth defeat in 10
